nd Biology. \niii. A/Level passes or equivalents in at least two (2) \nsubjects from Physics, Chemistry, Biology and \nZoology. \niv. A degree in any health related subjects from a \nrecognised University  with a minimum entry \nrequirement for College of Medicine programme. \nv. Without prejudice to all requirements above, the \nDepartment may also conduct an interview for \nprospective candidates. \nFive O/Level credit passes in  English Language, \nMathematics, Biology, Chemistry and Physics. \nEnglish Language, Biology, \nChemistry and Physics. \nPHYSIOTHERAPY i.  JUPEB/A\u2019 L evel passes i n Physics, Chemistry \nand Biology. \n \nii. B.Sc. Degree  (First Class/Second Class  Upper) \nin Medical related fields \nFive O/Level credit passes in  English Language, \nMathematics, Biology, Chemistry and Physics. \nEnglish Language, Biology, \nChemistry and Physics. \nRADIOGRAPHY \n \nPasses in three (3) JUPEB/A' Level subjects:  \nPhysics, Chemistry and Biology. \nFive O/Level credit passes in  English Language, \nMathematics, Biology, Chemistry and Physics. \nEnglish Language, Biology, \nChemistry and Physics. \n** DE CANDIDATES MUST SATISFY ALL O/LEVEL REQUIREMENTS. \n\n8 \n \n \n \nFACULTY OF DENTAL SCIENCES \nDEPARTMENT DIRECT ENTRY REQUIREMENTS UTME REQUIREMENTS UTME SUBJECTS \nDENTISTRY i.  JUPEB/A\u2019 L evel passes in Physics Chemistry \nand Biology. \n \nii. B.Sc. Degree  (First Class/Second Class  Upper) \nin Medical related fields \nFive O/Level credit passes in  English Language, \nMathematics, Biology, Chemistry and Physics. \nEnglish Language, Biology, \nChemistry and Physics. \n** DE CANDIDATES MUST SATISFY ALL O/LEVEL REQUIREMENTS.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 9994, "end_char_idx": 12419, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "de955308-2797-4d4b-a3ea-932cf2b6e24a": {"__data__": {"id_": "de955308-2797-4d4b-a3ea-932cf2b6e24a", "embedding": null, "metada