 Scie nce and \nIntegrated Science).  \nUNILAG does not accept Commerce, CRS/IRS \nand Financial Accounting. \nEnglish Language and any three \nsubjects from Mathematics, \nBiology, Physics, Chemistry, \nEconomics, Government, and \nLiterature-in-English. \nPUBLIC \nADMINISTRATION \nVery good passes in JUPEB/A\u2019Level subjects: \nGovernment/Civic Education/History, Economics \nand any other Social Sciences or Art subjects \n \nFive \u2018O\u2019 Level credit passes in \nEnglish Language, Mathematics, \nGovernment/Civic Education/History, Economics \nand any other Social Sciences or Arts subject.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 5428, "end_char_idx": 10722, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "745120f8-11a4-4ab6-a1a2-fb23743ca631": {"__data__": {"id_": "745120f8-11a4-4ab6-a1a2-fb23743ca631", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"page_label": "1", "file_name": "unilag_2024-2025_Admission_Requirements.pdf", "file_path": "data/unilag_2024-2025_Admission_Requirements.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 527929, "creation_date": "2025-07-31", "last_modified_date": "2025-07-31", "source_type": "file", "page_count": 27, "edubot_metadata": {"document_id": "53755f4a-eb91-411e-9c83-1b13f6cf4435", "date_uploaded": "2025-07-31T12:17:00.422043", "title": "2024/2025 Admission Requirements", "summary": "This document outlines the admission requirements for the University of Lagos for the 2024/2025 academic year.  It details entry requirements for various departments within different faculties, including UTME requirements, direct entry requirements (JUPEB/A' Level, HND/OND, NCE, Diplomas), and O'Level requirements.  Specific subject combinations are listed for each department.", "source": {"organization": "University of Lagos", "url": null, "authority_tier": 3, "reliability_score": 1.0}, "temporal": {"publication_date": null, "last_updated": null, "validity_period": "2024/20