lish \nLanguage, Mathematics,  and any two of \nEconomics, Government/History, Civic \nEducation, Geography and any one of Literature-\nin-English, CRK/IRK and any Nigerian \nLanguage. \nEnglish Language, two Social \nSciences and one Arts subject. \n **Mathematics is accepted. \n \n \n** DE CANDIDATES MUST SATISFY ALL O/LEVEL REQUIREMENTS.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 10724, "end_char_idx": 12836, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "9df12fba-6bb6-4248-90e3-5450df4faa82": {"__data__": {"id_": "9df12fba-6bb6-4248-90e3-5450df4faa82", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"page_label": "1", "file_name": "unilag_2024-2025_Admission_Requirements.pdf", "file_path": "data/unilag_2024-2025_Admission_Requirements.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 527929, "creation_date": "2025-07-31", "last_modified_date": "2025-07-31", "source_type": "file", "page_count": 27, "edubot_metadata": {"document_id": "2b3fc38d-332c-43e3-8714-5c1217f0322b", "date_uploaded": "2025-07-31T12:18:03.362547", "title": "2024/2025 Admission Requirements", "summary": "This document outlines the admission requirements for the University of Lagos for the 2024/2025 academic year.  It details entry requirements for various departments across multiple faculties, including UTME requirements, direct entry requirements (JUPEB/A' Level, HND/OND, NCE, diplomas), and O'Level requirements.", "source": {"organization": "University of Lagos", "url": null, "authority_tier": 3, "reliability_score": 1.0}, "temporal": {"publication_date": null, "last_updated": null, "validity_period": "2024/2025", "version": null}, "classification": {"education_level": ["tertiary"], "content_type": "admission", "subject_areas": ["Arts", "Basic Medical Sciences", "Clinical Sciences", "Dental Sciences", "Education", "Engineering", "Environmental Sciences", "Law", "Management Sciences", "Pharmacy", "Science", "Social Sciences", "The