athematics and Biology.  \n \n \nSOCIAL WORK i. Very good pa sses in three JUPEB/A\u2019 Level \nsubjects: Economics, Government, \nGeography, History and CRS/IRS. \n \nii. University of Lagos Diploma in Social \nDevelopment and Administration (SDA). \nFive \u2018O\u2019 Level credit passes in English \nLanguage, Mathematics, and any two of \nEconomics, Government/History, Civic \nEducation and Geography and one of Literature -\nin-English, CRK/IRK, any Nigerian Language \nand Biology. \n \nEnglish Language, two Social \nSciences subjects and one Arts \nsubject.  \n**Mathematics is accepted. \n \n\n27 \n \nSOCIOLOGY i. Very good pass es in three JUPEB/A\u2019 Level \nsubjects: Economics, Government, \nGeography, History and CRS/IRS. \n \nii. University of Lagos Diploma in Social \nDevelopment and Administration (SDA). \nFive \u2018O\u2019 Level credit passes in English \nLanguage, Mathematics,  and any two of \nEconomics, Government/History, Civic \nEducation, Geography and any one of Literature-\nin-English, CRK/IRK and any Nigerian \nLanguage. \nEnglish Language, two Social \nSciences and one Arts subject. \n **Mathematics is accepted. \n \n \n** DE CANDIDATES MUST SATISFY ALL O/LEVEL REQUIREMENTS.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 28505, "end_char_idx": 54723, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "be07f56e-5161-4302-9c83-a76a48b308e3": {"__data__": {"id_": "be07f56e-5161-4302-9c83-a76a48b308e3", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"page_label": "1", "file_name": "unilag_2024-2025_Admission_Requirements.pdf", "file_path": "data/unilag_2024-2025_Admission_Requirements.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 527929, "creation_date": "2025-07-31", "last_modified_date": "2025-07-31", "source_type": "file", "page_count": 27, "edubot_metadata": {"document_id": "2b3fc38d-332c-43e3-8714-5c1217f0322b", "date_uploaded": "2025-07-31T12:18:03.362547", "title": "2024/2025 Adm