it in: Islamic Studies. \nii. Very good passes in three JUPEB subject: IRS \nand any two of Government/History, Literature-in-\nEnglish, French, Yoruba/Igbo and Economics. \niii. Three \u2018A\u2019 Level passes in relevant teaching \nsubject areas. \n \n \n \n \nFive O/Level credit passes in  English, \nMathematics, Geography and any two subjects \nfrom Science or Social Sciences. \n \n \n \n \n \nFive O/Level credit passes in  English Language, \nMathematics, History/Government and any two \nsubjects from Arts or Social Sciences. \n \n \n \n \n \nFive O/Level credit passes in  English Language, \nMathematics, any three subjects from Arts, \nScience and Social Sciences.  \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \nFive O/Level credit passes in  English Language, \nMathematics, Islamic Religious Studies (IRS) \nand two of Literature -in-English, any Nigerian \nLanguage, History/Government, French/A rabic, \nEconomics/Commerce, Civic Education/Social \nStudies. \n \n \n \n \nEnglish language and any three of \nLiterature-in-English, History/ \nGovernment, French/Arabic, \nGeography, Mathematics, any \nNigerian Language, CRS/IRS, \nEconomics/Commerce. \n \n \nEnglish language and any three \nsubjects from Arts or Social \nSciences. \n \n \n \n \n \nEnglish Language and any three \nsubjects from Arts or Social \nSciences.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 9988, "end_char_idx": 12855, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "24c615b2-9d26-46ea-8e79-52b5d60b0f10": {"__data__": {"id_": "24c615b2-9d26-46ea-8e79-52b5d60b0f10", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"page_label": "1", "file_name": "unilag_2024-2025_Admission_Requirements.pdf", "file_path": "data/unilag_2024-2025_Admission_Requirements.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 527929, "creation_date": "2025-07-31", "last_modified_date": "2025-07-31", "source_type": "file", "page_count": 27, "edubot_metadata": {"document_id": "2b3fc38